{
    "name": "Mento",
    "description": "Decentralized multi-currency stablecoin platform and onchain FX exchange. Uses Fixed-Price Market Makers (FPMMs) quoting oracle rates to enable swaps between stablecoins (e.g. USDm/GBPm) at real-world FX prices.",
